<div class="hero">
    <h1>Grassroots Innovation for a More Innovative and Intelligent Africa</h1>
</div>

<section id="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>AI Bridge Africa is a grassroots initiative focused on closing the artificial intelligence gap across the continent by empowering youth and communities with access to AI education, tools, and opportunities.</p>
</section>

<section id="mission">
    <h2>Mission</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to build a more intelligent and equitable Africa by fostering grassroots innovation, inclusive education, and community-driven AI solutions that address local challenges.</p>
</section>

<section id="programs">
    <h2>Programs</h2>
    <p>We run AI literacy workshops, mentorship programs, innovation labs, and hackathons to equip young Africans with the skills and confidence to lead in the AI era.</p>
</section>

<section id="partners">
    <h2>Partners</h2>
    <p>We collaborate with educational institutions, tech companies, NGOs, and community leaders to expand our reach and impact across Africa.</p>
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
